# The backend image copies only pyproject.toml, uv.lock, README.md and
# knowledge/ — nothing from infra/. Excluding the whole dir keeps CDK synth
# output (cdk.out and any variant) out of the Docker build context, which is
# the repo root; otherwise the output dir nests into itself infinitely.
